音频 


git pull
git checkout audio/stack_on_psram_v3.3
git submodule update --init --recursive

ADF : master
Example : https://github.com/espressif/esp-adf/tree/master/examples/player/pipeline_a2dp_sink_stream

btw: the specific branch audio/stack_on_psram_v3.3 should use lyrat development board with ESP32-WROVER-E module
and you must set CONFIG_ESP32_REV_MIN=3 in your sdkconfig.